Package org.gvsig.mapsheets.layout

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MapSheetFrameView
    Special view frame to prevent the user from resizing it.
    MapSheetsFrameText
    Special text frame that keeps a text template with a wildcard.
    MapSheetsLayoutTemplate
    This subclass of Layout provides special behavior: can be associated to a grid; some of its components will can be refreshed with data from a single sheet.
    MapSheetsProjectMap
    This class is the gvsig document which holds the layout template as a field.
    MapSheetsProjectMapFactory
    Every gvsig document needs to have an associated factory.
